{"article_id":"THTds4vJ5m46IGDU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"After a mass shooting , a police chase and a shootout , a violent day in San Bernardino , Calif. , ended in the death of two suspects ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"authorities say .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"Syed Farook , 28 , and Tashfeen Malik , 27 , were responsible for the Wednesday morning attack","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"that killed at least 14 people and injured 21 ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"according to San Bernardino Police Chief Jarrod Burguan .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"After initial concerns","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that there could have been a third shooter ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"police are now confident","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"there were only two .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Thursday evening , authorities released the names of the 14 victims .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"The motives of the shooters remains unclear .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"But briefings from police reveal an hours-long timeline of events :","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Syed Rizwan Farook , an environmental specialist","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"who was born in the U.S. ,","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"had worked for the San Bernardino County health department for five years .","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"Tashfeen Malik , Farook 's wife , was in the U.S. on a K-1 visa","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"and had a Pakistani passport ,","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"according to David Bowdich of the FBI 's LA office .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"The couple had been married for about two years ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"says Hussam Ayloush of the Council on American-Islamic Relations .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"They had a 6-month-old daughter ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"whom they left with Farook 's mother on the morning of the attack ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Ayloush says .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Ayloush notes","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that Farook and Malik were both Muslims","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and their families said","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"they showed no sign of fanaticism .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"He emphasizes","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"that the attackers ' motives remain unknown .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Neither had a criminal record","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that police are aware of ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Burguan says .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Patrick Baccari worked with Syed Rizwan Farook for two years .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"He told NPR 's Kelly McEvers","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"though Farook was quiet ,","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"he `` assumed","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"Syed was our friend . '' `` As I 'm pulling the paper towels from the dispenser","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"there 's explosions ,","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"there 's bullets","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"flying through the walls .","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"I look at myself in the mirror","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"and see the blood .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"I thought","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"somebody booby-trapped the towels dispenser , ''","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Baccari said .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"He and three others stayed in the restroom","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"until officers arrived .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Farook 's brother , Syed Raheel Farook , served in the Navy from 2003 to 2007 ,","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"a Navy spokeswoman confirmed to NPR .","depth":4},{"id":50,"text":"Syed Raheel Farook completed his service as an information systems technician 3rd class , a junior enlisted sailor ,","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"and he was attached to the crew of the aircraft carrier USS Enterprise .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Navy records indicate","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"that he made at least one deployment aboard the Enterprise to the Middle East .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"The attack began on Wednesday morning , at an office holiday party in the Inland Regional Center in San Bernardino .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"The center provides social services to residents with developmental disabilities ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"but the shooting was focused on an office party for San Bernardino County staff .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Burguan at a press conference late Thursday","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"that 75 to 80 people were in the room .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"As a county employee , Farook was at the party .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"At some point he left in anger ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Burguan says .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Both were dressed in `` tactical gear ''","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"( including load-bearing vests , but not ballistic or bulletproof vests )","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"and carrying .223-caliber assault-style rifles and semiautomatic handguns ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"police say .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"The weapons","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"used in the shooting","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"were legally purchased ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"Burguan says :","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"The handguns were purchased by Farook ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"and authorities are still investigating","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"who purchased the rifles .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"Farook and Malik entered the Inland Regional Center","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"and fired between 65 and 75 rifle rounds ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Burguan said Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"A bomb","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"- three explosive devices ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"linked to a remote control car","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"and placed inside a bag -","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"was also discovered at the shooting site ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"but it failed to go off ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Burguan said .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"At least 14 people died","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"and 21 were wounded in the initial attack .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Emergency response teams rushed to the facility .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Approximately 300 officers were part of that response ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Burguan said .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Lt. Mike Madden was one of the first responders on the scene .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"At the press conference late Thursday , he described the `` surreal '' scene .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Listen here :","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"As the search for the suspects began ,","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"hundreds of people were evacuated from the Inland Regional Center .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Farook was wearing a ski mask at the time of the shooting ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"law enforcement officials tell NPR 's Dina Temple-Raston ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"but witnesses to the shooting still recognized him .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"Based on those eyewitness accounts ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"police drove to nearby Redlands , to a house","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"that had both Farook and Malik 's names on the rental agreement .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"( Member station KPCC has a map of the locations","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"involved in the attack . )","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Police ca n't confirm","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"whether Farook and Malik lived in the house .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"At the house , police encountered Farook and Malik ,","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"driving a black Ford SUV .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"The car was a rental ,","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"the police said Thursday .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"Farook and Malik drove off in the SUV ,","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"and police pursued .","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"The car chase ended in a shootout .","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"Law enforcement officers fired approximately 380 rounds at the car ;","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"the suspects fired around 76 rounds at the officers .","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"The suspects had over 1,400 .223-caliber rounds either on their person or in their vehicle ,","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"Buergan says ,","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"and over 200 9-mm rounds .","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"Hours after the attack began ,","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"the two suspects were dead .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"Two officers suffered injuries","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"that are not life-threatening .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"A third person was taken in custody ;","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"police have determined","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"he was not involved in the shooting","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"and is not a suspect .","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"The FBI is leading an investigation into the attackers ' motives and planning .","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"An armored vehicle with a battering ram attached `` very slowly and methodically '' broke down the door of the house in Redlands on Wednesday night ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"a witness told the LA Times .","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"Police discovered a stockpile of ammunition and explosives inside the house ,","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"Burguan said Thursday ,","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"including thousands of rifle and handgun rounds and 12 pipe bombs , with the materials and tools","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"to create more .","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"Investigators also removed thumb drives , cellphones and other electronic items from the house ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"Burguan said .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"Authorities also continue to examine the site of the shooting at Inland Regional Center and the site of the shootout at the SUV .","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"All of the agencies","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"involved in the investigation","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"emphasize","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"that they have not identified a motive for the shooting .","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"The FBI has tasked counterterrorism agents to the case ,","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"NPR 's Carrie Johnson reports ,","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"but has not yet determined","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"whether the attack was in fact an act of terrorism .","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"Carrie also says","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"a source tells her","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"Farook had some electronic contact with people overseas","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"who were on the radar of U.S. national security officials ,","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"but that investigators are still trying to work out the significance of that contact .","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"Whatever the motive , Burguan , the San Bernardino police chief , says","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"there does appear to have been some form of planning","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"involved in the attack .","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"they just ran home ,","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"put on these types of tactical clothes ,","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"grabbed guns","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"and came back on a spur-of-the-moment thing , ''","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"he said Wednesday .","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"President Obama made a statement from the Oval Office on Thursday ,","depth":6},{"id":156,"text":"noting","depth":7},{"id":157,"text":"that it `` may take some time '' for investigators to conduct interviews","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"and sort through the evidence .","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"He again emphasized","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"that the motive is not yet clear ,","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"investigators have not ruled out terrorism , a workplace-related shooting or a mixed-motive attack .","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"`` Rest assured","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"that we will get to the bottom of this , ''","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":166,"text":"San Bernardino Mayor Carey Davis said in a statement","depth":5},{"id":167,"text":"that the attack `` has shaken the core of our community . ''","depth":5},{"id":168,"text":"The county suspended all nonessential county services for Thursday and Friday .","depth":4},{"id":169,"text":"Late Wednesday , Farook 's brother-in-law , Farhan Khan , appeared at a press conference with the Council on American-Islamic Relations","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"( CAIR )","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"for Greater LA","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"he had no idea","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"why Farook would carry out such an attack .","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"`` I just can not express how sad I am for what happened today , ''","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"He wished victims a speedy recovery","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"he was in shock over the shooting ,","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"according to member station KPCC .","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"`` We unequivocally condemn the horrific act","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"that happened today , ''","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"Ayloush , the executive director of the LA CAIR office , said at the same conference ,","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"speaking on behalf of the local Muslim community .","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"`` We offer our heartfelt prayers and condolences to the injured , to the families of those","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"who have been killed .","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"... We stand in mourning , in sadness , for what happened . ''","depth":7},{"id":188,"text":"President Obama , in an interview on CBS on Wednesday night , called for changes to America 's gun control laws ,","depth":7},{"id":189,"text":"as he has after mass shootings at Newtown , Conn. ; Tucson , Ariz. ; Fort Hood , Texas ; Charleston , S.C. ; and Colorado Springs , Colo. , among others .","depth":7},{"id":190,"text":"On Thursday , he reiterated his calls","depth":7},{"id":191,"text":"to make it harder for people to acquire weapons .","depth":7},{"id":192,"text":"And in a press conference Thursday morning , U.S. Attorney General Loretta Lynch said","depth":6},{"id":193,"text":"violence like the San Bernardino shooting `` has no place in this country . '' `` This is not what we stand for , ''","depth":7},{"id":194,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":195,"text":"`` This is not what we live for . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":391,"left":249,"right":390,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":243,"right":248,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":205,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":204,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":200,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":197,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":198,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":201,"right":202,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":201,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":242,"left":226,"right":241,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":226,"left":221,"right":225,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":221,"left":217,"right":220,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":206,"right":216,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":206,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":216,"left":213,"right":215,"relation":"joint","nuclearity